            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Calpurnus <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> veteranus <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> dominapus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Weihung an den Passgott ist verbunden mit derjenigen an die Matres - Matronae. (B): Grenier: Z. 3: dominica&amp;lt;b=P&amp;gt;us; &amp;quot;&amp;quot;dominapus&amp;quot;&amp;quot; is considered by Barocelli (InscrIt) the less used form for &amp;quot;&amp;quot;dominabus&amp;quot;&amp;quot;, in dativ, referred to the Matronae.</p>
            </div>
